Source: pgedge-nla
Section: database
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Muhammad Aqeel <muhammad.aqeel@pgedge.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13)
Standards-Version: 4.1.3
Homepage: https://github.com/pgEdge/pgedge-postgres-mcp

Package: pgedge-postgres-mcp
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: pgEdge Natural Language Agent - MCP Server
 Model Context Protocol (MCP) server that enables natural language
 queries against PostgreSQL databases. Provides HTTP/HTTPS API with read-only
 query execution, schema analysis, and semantic search capabilities.

Package: pgedge-nla-cli
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, pgedge-postgres-mcp (= ${binary:Version})
Description: pgEdge Natural Language Agent - CLI Client
 Command-line chat client for interacting with PostgreSQL databases
 using natural language. Connects to Natural Language Agent and supports
 multiple LLM providers (Anthropic Claude, OpenAI, Ollama).

Package: pgedge-nla-web
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, pgedge-postgres-mcp (= ${source:Version}), python3, nginx
Description: pgEdge Natural Language Agent - Web UI
 Modern React-based web interface for the pgEdge Natural Language
 Agent. Provides an intuitive UI for natural language database queries,
 monitoring, and administration.
